{"type": "article", "id": 59349, "title": "一款易于抓握的圆珠笔，享受顺滑质感｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-12-16T22:57:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 55131, "name": "Studio Más"}, {"id": 34361, "name": "Land Rover"}, {"id": 55132, "name": "ZEBRA"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 55133, "name": "Sanna Völker"}, {"id": 55134, "name": "Teddy Schuyers"}, {"id": 30, "name": "Paul Smith"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 82, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181216213743r2HTBSgUwo50l8qn.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #2965a8; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #2965a8} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>bLen by Nendo for ZEBRA</h3><p>日本设计工作室 Nendo 与日本制笔品牌 Zebra 展开合作，共同推出了一款名为 bLen 的圆珠笔，主要关注构成书写过程的微妙动作。</p><p>针对这一问题，Nendo 设计了一款书写工具，目的是提供尽可能流畅的书写体验，让使用者在刻画直线、小曲线甚至文字间的中断部分时都能充分享受顺滑质感。Nendo 赋予这款圆珠笔稳固结实的外观，其形状易于抓握，因而长时间使用也依然舒适。</p><p>笔夹被设计为扁平式，与笔身形状完美贴合，在书写时能保持稳定平衡，按动钮则设计为宽且扁平的形状，按动起来十分方便。据悉，这款圆珠笔共有黑色、红色和蓝色三种墨水颜色以及 0.5 毫米和 0.7 毫米两种笔尖可供选择，设计者还将笔的技术信息展示在按动钮上，这样的设计让人联想到专业绘图工具。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812162139559cxkunBtKV5jhmH0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216213956FB8K5YELSXPQ0Ikw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216213956Oz3w6de1FLUp9Qix.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216213956KPr3dBEe6ZtjcIbR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812162139556QG1dl4UqXWPOkLx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216213957YPmyV4c8TGI9WzdK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216213956CRhoZf4jGLdlJW5q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/blen/?erelease\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nendo</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Defender 90 1:43 Die Cast Metal Collector's Edition by Paul Smith + Land Rover</h3><p>2015 年 Paul Smith 与 Land Rover 合作，以英国郊外为主题打造了全球唯一一台、集合了 27 种颜色的 Multi-color Defender 90，加上专门订制的内饰，除非自行配色，否则几乎是没有可能拥有它的。</p><p>要拥有真车或者是天方夜谭，但最近 Paul Smith 就联同 Almost Real 及 Sum’s Model Toys Co 工作室携手创造了这台 Paul Smith + Land Rover Defender 90 的模型车，比例为 1:43，适合摆放在家里观赏。售价 75 美元，<a href=\"https://www.paulsmith.com/us/paul-smith-land-rover-defender-90-1-43-die-cast-metal-collector-s-edition?utm_source=linkshare&amp;utm_medium=affiliates&amp;utm_content=QFGLnEolOWg&amp;utm_campaign=15&amp;ranMID=39528&amp;ranEAID=QFGLnEolOWg&amp;ranSiteID=QFGLnEolOWg-fnniapQfCu8wlFaU.ktOCw\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买。</a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216214101hA0YuF4I86gTPB1N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812162141023nhUvOAfMiuGqQbc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216214102hfVYPyawX6HGWlIU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216214101f39T2xYeymG1Eb5s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216214101FysjYO9wnUtaJdzD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216214103zAyjGJt8apXoIUmR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lamp Más by Studio Más</h3><p>Studio Más 以设计简单而独特的产品和家具而闻名，最近他们刚发布了他们的最新产品 Lamp Más。Lamp Más 专为 2018 年的 Young Retro 首尔设计节而设计，其灵感来自于模拟行为和复古的色彩和形状，旨在实现拉线开关和灯体之间的美妙平衡。</p><p>你可能还会联想到 Alexander Calder 的作品，他以创造移动是雕塑而闻名，这些雕塑本身就受蒙德里安的启发。Studio Más 重新诠释了 Alexander Calder 的想法，结合灯光的作用，设计出了 Lamp Más，黑色灯体线条和彩色圆形开关碰撞出不一样的趣味。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216214156CQlON7eEt6ZoPm21.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799506\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216214133W9RPLb5s7z8ntYHT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216214133ifaNWl63TvZrOub1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666896\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216214133c0OdHwvJjqBz8RWy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666400\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.designstudiomas.com/product/detail_new.html?product_no=100&amp;cate_no=1&amp;display_group=2\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studio Más</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Guts by Teddy Schuyers</h3><p>好的设计，能减轻病人的心理负担。设计师 Teddy Schuyers 推出的这款造口袋Guts，一改肠造口（stoma bag）的设计，并透过访问多个患者，设计出贴合日常、运动及亲密时刻用的三个款式，用上无声物料及排气口，减低使用者的尴尬。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216214249W6t829AbG40URnwL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666800\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216214249htb2LKM1scAnFaVH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.653600\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216214249k1OpirAXH87ZuPyL.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666800\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.teddyschuyers.com/#/guts/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Teddy Schuyers</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Snug candle holders by Sanna Völker</h3><p>Snug 系列烛台由经验丰富的石匠手工打造而成。每款烛台均采用天然的石料制成，其中一些石材的历史长达 5 亿年。这些石材由设计师 Sanna Völker 亲自从巴塞罗那一座小山村的采石场里挑选出来，旨在突显当地的手工工艺，以及材料中所蕴含的情感价值。</p><p>两根蜡烛被固定在石制的体块上，这种由材料本身带来的“束缚”传递出一种粗糙而又精致的感觉。Snug 讲述的是关于工艺、可持续和透明度的故事，它隐藏在作品背后，并且与作品拥有着相同的美感。售价 115 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.sannavolker.com/shop\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812162143363e7vyx9hmIQ6HJAi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216214336FcgRJQZz0aVvr94d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216214336Tl0nCMyc7qKkH2hZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216214336wsxj3ybQ4rCtcpo9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216214336yHrNSd5cpKxFnWV3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216214337lWVkuPTM7RLKJzvt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497981\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812162143372xceK1iXdR49IHJD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181216214337CdxSeqNlOzbFAiWy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}